# TQ-2: Test Failure Diagnosis
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: Any failing test

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Test Failure: A test not passing expected assertions.

ENFORCE: Every test failure must be investigated to determine whether code or test is at fault before any fix is applied.
PROHIBIT: Ignoring failures; guessing cause without analysis; deleting a failing test without diagnosis.
ON VIOLATION: Halt deployment → escalate to responsible engineer and QA Skill.
